pan style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">The only scientific way a product can be judged is on past performance. Past performance is the means by which future performance is estimated. All of the existing evidence tells us that GM will lead to reduced yields and reduced levels of nutrition. Farmers will produce less and what they produce will be less nutritious.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">The introduction of GM agriculture into the UK will make the UK more </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">dependant</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> on imports. It will also make British exports of food less competitive and will have a negative impact upon the Balance of Payments.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">To argue that GM will increase yield based only on absurd hope with no supporting evidence is not merely unscientific, it is negligent. Such uninformed attitudes will lead British agriculture towards catastrophe.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">If agricultural crops which are grown in the UK are patented and owned by foreign multinational corporations when what we have in the UK is food insecurity because we do not have control over own food production. GM or genetically-modified food equals food insecurity; biodiversity gives us food security.</span><a name="_GoBack"></a><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Â  </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">November 2013 </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div></body></html>